{"tid":993561,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲深受飛蚊症困擾","createTime":"2019-01-24T04:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T05:22:15.000Z","uid":53624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0b748b0c4c5772f3f7945eb1a36e3665a8ddad8b","tid":993561,"uid":53624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"小弟廿頭 已經有飛蚊幾年<br />\n本身得一粒黑點 慢慢一條條咁增加 而加左右眼都各10粒左右<br />\n好影響心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日頭盡量都唔想出街見到啲蚊<br />\n自己做左好多資料搜集 知道無得自己好 <br />\nLaser 係廢既 唯一有用既玻璃體切除手術又貴到比唔起<br />\n真係覺得好灰 有幾次攞住枝筆望左幾分鐘 <br />\n真係想插盲自己算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人明白我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87850a713ce91be5359749f5b35c745333fa268","tid":993561,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"食下藍莓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b00e3d26b9529274c4c905d4062971e1f6f6517","tid":993561,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"我明，驗過良性之後迫自己接受同面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608fd3e4798f4ebd80ff12dcafb22f5aa50d39e4","tid":993561,"uid":161374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"好細個就有 所以習慣咗，個腦自然會無視"},{"pid":"ef9472e358b70f1a80b2dc7114e696443d2d7745","tid":993561,"uid":53624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f87850a713ce91be5359749f5b35c745333fa268","tid":993561,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"食下藍莓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"唔會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile